		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Kreigdrache&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Hey everyone.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have been away from everquest for a while.  I quit and then rejoined then quit again.  They never had a class I really enjoyed.  But now it looks like they do, a warrior that ACTUALLY does damage =).  So I am thinking of rejoining and had a few questions on making a zerker.<br /><br />1) What races can be zerkers?<br />**Doh! this one was answered a few posts down, guess I missed it in my first read over the forums.<br />2) What are the weapon restrictions on zerkers?<br />3) I will most likely not be able to twink him, so can anyone give me some advice on where to lvl him so that I can make some cash and get him some gear?  Oh, I prefer to solo until the upper lvls 45+ if possible.<br /><br />Any answers would be greatly appreciated.<br /><br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Mar 27 17:29:10 2004 by Kreigdrache</span></i><br /><br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Mar 27 17:29:19 2004 by Kreigdrache</span></i></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >1 Replies</td></tr></table>
